  "claim_short": "For every fixed M, the subcase N-n <= M has a deterministic positive answer: whenever the vectors X_1,...,X_N span R^n, the space (R^n, ||.||_{P_{N,n}}) has cotype 2 with constant depending only on M. The same bounded-codimension conclusion holds for projections of the standard cross-polytope.",
